Package civitas.celestis.world

Interface World<L,R,M extends Movable<L,R> & Tickable>

Type Parameters:
L - The datatype used to represent location in this world
R - The datatype used to represent rotation in this world
M - The type of movable object this world contains
All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<M>, Nameable<String>, Tickable, Unique<UUID>
All Known Subinterfaces:
BigWorld2<O>, BigWorld3<O>, SingleWorld2<O>, SingleWorld3<O>, World2<O>, World3<O>
public interface World<L,R,M extends Movable<L,R> & Tickable> extends Iterable<M>, Unique<UUID>, Nameable<String>, Tickable
Represents an in-game world.
